name: The Banyumas Villa
address: Jl. Tukad Banyumas No.1, Dauh Puri Klod, Kec. Denpasar Bar., Kota Denpasar, Bali 80225, Indonesia
review 1:
It's located in residential area, Renon. So not many brilliant touristic restaurants option around this hotel  but it have restaurant in front of medium size of pool.
Staffs have really good English and well trained for smooth operation.
I took the room for 4people, it's spacious with maisonette style, but no balcony and feel bit suffocated. Kitchen and tiny laundry drying space is available. No bathtub.
review 2:
Stayed here for the nyepi package.
Everything's good for it's price range. Very worth la.
The room, the service, the pool, all's good.
Just the staff forgot about the 15% discount for FnB, but I think I find that kind of problem everywhere around here.

Maybe I'll go here again.
review 3:
Stayed four time in here
We love it here..Feels like home..
But Sometime we got good room (when we got lucky)
And Sometime we got the room need to have more attention to detail..like the switch or the power point almost falling down to the floor, the air-conditioning is not cold enough for big room..

But anyway overall
We love to stay here..
See you next trip
review 4:
Nice hotel, great staff, clean,comfort and wonderful
Thank you, and we will back
review 5: Excellent and safe place, nice restaurant with affordable prices, tasty breakfast. Restaurant working hours 7-22. Very clean swimming pool, clean rooms. Print and copy service for customers at reception. The best villa in center of Denpasar city.

name: Rumah Rakyat (coffee & working space)
address: Jl. Tukad Melangit No.21, Panjer, Denpasar Selatan, Kota Denpasar, Bali 80234, Indonesia
review 1:
The place has many rooms with tables and chairs. It has good coffee and tea but the food is so sad. I ordered roti bakar, and it looked unwell cooked. It's better to buy roti bakar in the night market at a reasonable price.

It has a wide parking area for motorbikes.

The owner also needs to pay more attention to the cleanliness of their place. Many dust and the toilet is so dirty and smelly. It was like everyone peed on the floor.
review 2: Their private rooms really accommodate small meetings. Beverages are quite good, but the public space is too packed with cigarette smoke.
review 3: their canai is crispy enough, good hot latte, the service so so, they gave us a wrong order 2 times (maybe because one of them still training)
review 4: Amazing space for deep focus or hanging out! Affordable price with tasty drinks and snacks. SUPER FAST wifi!
review 5: Sufficient parking lot especially for motorbike, good vibe. Affordable prices.

name: Warung Story
address: Jl. Tukad Sanghyang No.25, Panjer, Denpasar Selatan, Kota Denpasar, Bali 80234, Indonesia
review 1:
I like the their food and beverage but dislike their working space facilities. Their wifi speed was so bad and it cause me and my friend used our personal internet. They also haven't enough electrical plugins. But, their food was soooo tastyü§§i love their bakso ayam. It's really suitable with my tasteüëçüëç
Their parking area was large enough for 15 motorcycles and 4 cars inside. Ohya, they also provide some games such as uno card and uno stacko. You can play it with your friendsüòç
review 2: Great place. Very delicious, fresh cooked food. Drinks also really tasty. Friendly people in a nice little and very clean Warung.
review 3:
I like this place. There's a lot of dishes and drink you can try with a reasonable price. This place also helped me for my last 2 events. The staffs are friendly, and serve you right. There's also a memory of complicated person who stir my feeling into a literal mess, but that's another story. And like they say, another time another story.
PS : the owner is REALLY afraid of snakes
review 4: its a nice place, clean, comfortable, good food and drinks at affordable prices, will definitely come here again.

The food is so so. Been here twice. First day i order lychee tea, but it doesn‚Äôt taste fresh. I didn‚Äôt finish it. And second day i went with my bf. He ordered coffee and i ordered taro latte. But the place is really comfy. Even tho it‚Äôs pretty hot on the middle day. Proper parking lot. But they got only 1-2 spot for car.

first time here, like cafe in general. only different in photobooth.

food is too expensive, very quiet.

clean and aesthetic
